name: Bob
text: I'm Bob! A nice friendly guy working for the 'Red Company'

name: Bob
text: Me and my friends are out here chopping all these trees

name: Bob
text: Yeah, but we've got to somehow make profit!

name: You
text: Do you know by any chance, where we are?

name: Bob
text: Sure I do, you're smack dab in the middle of The great pines forest

name: You
text: Well thanks I guess.....,well I got to go! Catch you sometime later!
